  "experimental_data": {
    "key_results": "Sustained release of alogliptin achieved using bentonite with HPMC as binder. Release followed Fickian diffusion. XRD showed shift in montmorillonite peak indicating intercalation of drug, but HPMC helped maintain gel structure.",
